OL,3,CHydropower scheme celebrates 60 years
OL,4,Cof operations
OL,6,FA hydropower scheme near Aberystwyth
OL,7,Fis celebrating 60 years of operations
OL,8,Fthis month.
OL,10,FThe Rheidol Hydropower plant
OL,11,Fofficially opened its doors in 1964,
OL,12,Fcreating jobs and bringing electricity
OL,13,Fto many local homes for the first time.
OL,15,FCwm Rheidol and the surrounding area
OL,16,Fwas transformed six decades ago when
OL,17,Fthe Rheidol Hydropower Scheme was
OL,18,Fbuilt.JThe plant remains the largest
OL,19,Fof its kind in both England and Wales.
