OL,3,CHydropower scheme celebrates 60 years
OL,4,Cof operations
OL,6,FNantymoch Reservoir sits in the 162
OL,7,Fsquare kilometres managed by Rheidol
OL,8,FHydropower plant. It generates
OL,9,Frenewable energy by collecting rain
OL,10,Fwater that runs off the surrounding
OL,11,Fhills.
OL,13,FNancy Evans, who spent many years as a
OL,14,Ftour guide at the visitor centre,
OL,15,Fremembers the chapel and farm yard at
OL,16,FNantymoch, which were demolished to
OL,17,Fmake way for the reservoir.
