OL,6,FShe said: "I remember my father when
OL,7,Fwe were children saying that they were
OL,8,Ftalking about demolishing the chapel
OL,9,Fat Nantymoch.
OL,11,F"But he said, but I don't think that
OL,12,Fwe will ever see it in our time. Well,
OL,13,Fhe didn't but we did. So, that was my
OL,14,Ffirst memory. But I do remember a big
OL,15,Fhole where the power station is at the
OL,16,Fmoment."
