OL,3,CHydropower scheme celebrates 60 years
OL,4,Cof operations
OL,6,FTalking about how much has changed in
OL,7,Fthe hydropower scheme's 60 year
OL,8,Fhistory, Dennis Geyermann from Rheidol
OL,9,FHydropower Plant said: "It's called
OL,10,Frenewable energy these days.
OL,12,F"That's not the terminology which we
OL,13,Fused back in the sixties, even if I
OL,14,Fwasn't born at the time. It's very
OL,15,Fsustainable, you see.
OL,17,F"The impact of building a hydropower
OL,18,Fstation is massive in the beginning
OL,19,Fbut then it lasts for such a long time.
